      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(IdnaDomainVariant other)
        Compares an IdnaDomainVariant based, in order, on the user form and DNS form. Given that DNS form is generated from the user form, these two comparisons should yield identical results. However, since both values are provided externally this can't be guaranteed, hence both are compared.
